high_descs: Make a left to walk to the brown shelf.
Pick up the sponge from the brown shelf.
Turn around to walk to the kitchen island.
Set the sponge down on a white plate on the kitchen island.
Pick up the white plate with the sponge on it from the kitchen island.
Walk around the kitchen island to reach the stove.
Set the sponge and white plate down in the lower cabinet to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a sponge on a white plate to put away next to the stove in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the wooden shelves in front.
Pick up the green sponge on the second shelf from the bottom.
Turn around and go to the middle of the kitchen island on the left.
Place the green sponge on the white plate on the table near the edge.
Pick up the white plate with the green sponge on it.
Go around the island to the front of the cabinet on the left of the stove.
Place the white plate with the green sponge in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with the sponge into the cabinet..

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wooden shelves.
Pick up the sponge from the second shelf.
Turn around and walk to the counter on the left.
Put the sponge down on the white plate.
Pick up the plate from the counter.
Walk over to the cabinet below the counter to the left of the oven.
Open the cabinet door, put the stack inside the cabinet, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move a stack into the cabinet.
